; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the recompute path (after fixated cost resolution) with a
; virtual posting that doesn't must_balance (unbalanced virtual).
; The (Virtual) posting is skipped by must_balance

2024/03/01 Fixated with virtual
    Assets:EUR        100 EUR {=$1.10}
    Assets:Checking  $-110.00
    (Budget:Notes)    $50.00

test bal
            $-110.00
             100 EUR  Assets
            $-110.00    Checking
             100 EUR    EUR
              $50.00  Budget:Notes
--------------------
             $-60.00
             100 EUR
end test
